&lt;p&gt;So I want to compare notes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you‚Äôre a newer developer with solid projects, are you also struggling to get hired? What feedback (if any) are you getting? Do you feel the bar has moved, or are we missing something important?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Would genuinely like to hear what others are seeing.&lt;/p&gt;

