&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Medical reports are notoriously messy‚Äîtables, signatures, and weird formatting. We use &lt;code&gt;PyMuPDF&lt;/code&gt; for its speed and reliability in extracting clean text.&lt;br&gt;
