&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As you probably noticed before, every &lt;code&gt;xyz:machine/*&lt;/code&gt; function has &lt;code&gt;cabi_post_xyz:machine/*&lt;/code&gt; pair.&lt;br&gt;
