&lt;h2&gt;Next.js Finally Has Competition&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Elvis Sautet „Éª Feb 15&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="ltag__link__taglist"&gt;
&lt;span class="ltag__link__tag"&gt;#nextjs&lt;/span&gt;
